        "text": "Such a clear acknowledgment, emanating from the head of our nation might divert mankind's\nattention from the spectre of impending atomic war. It could lift the consciousness of\nthis earth to a Cosmic level where a complete new set of Spiritual, scientific\nand Social values would be within the reach of all."
